<div class="faq">
    <h1>Frequently asked questions</h1>
    <details>
        <summary>Can I have a lost item delivered to me?</summary>
        <div>
            The Ride app helps provide a delivery solution that can save you a trip across town, whether it’s for a last-minute birthday gift or your forgotten keys. Just choose Package in the ride app.
            <a href="#">Get details</a>
        </div>
    </details>

    <details>
        <summary>Can I rent a car using Ride</summary>
        <div>
            Yes. <a href="#">Find out more</a> about how car rentals work.
        </div>
    </details>

    <details>
        <summary>Can I request a ride that picks up friends in different locations?</summary>
        <div>
            Yes. Set up a group ride in the ride app, invite your friends, and arrive at your destination together.
            <br> <a href="#">Learn more</a>
        </div>
    </details>

    <details>
        <summary>Can I request a taxi on Ride?</summary>
        <div>
            Ride makes it easy to get a taxi nearby in the cities where Ride Taxi is available. There’s no need to find a cab stand, hail a cab on the street, or even call the local cab company. Instead, you can use the Ride app or website to request a taxi in just a few taps or clicks.
            <br> <a href="#">Learn about requesting a taxi</a>
        </div>
    </details>
</div>

